600
00:26:38,000 --> 00:26:39,360
But I never managed to.

601
00:26:39,360 --> 00:26:41,280
This business keeps me tied down.

602
00:26:42,560 --> 00:26:43,840
Ever since I met you,

603
00:26:43,840 --> 00:26:45,120
I started seeing hope.

604
00:26:45,480 --> 00:26:46,240
I figure

605
00:26:46,840 --> 00:26:47,720
if you and Cong

606
00:26:47,960 --> 00:26:49,280
make things official soon,

607
00:26:49,520 --> 00:26:50,680
and get married,

608
00:26:51,080 --> 00:26:53,720
