620
00:27:16,320 --> 00:27:17,600
See this photo?

621
00:27:17,840 --> 00:27:19,160
After that photo exhibit,

622
00:27:19,160 --> 00:27:20,720
I kept looking for this photo of you.

623
00:27:21,280 --> 00:27:22,560
And I finally found it.

624
00:27:22,960 --> 00:27:24,080
