628
00:27:32,080 --> 00:27:33,080
Actually,

629
00:27:33,760 --> 00:27:35,720
I'd just started as a flight attendant.

630
00:27:35,960 --> 00:27:38,360
I was seeing so much around me,

631
00:27:39,080 --> 00:27:40,560
and I was stuck

632
00:27:41,120 --> 00:27:42,320
in this place of inner conflict,

633
00:27:42,680 --> 00:27:44,080
