640
00:28:17,600 --> 00:28:18,640
Zihan.

641
00:28:19,720 --> 00:28:20,920
Tao!

642
00:28:21,400 --> 00:28:22,960
Come on, I'll take you to the airport.

643
00:28:23,440 --> 00:28:24,040
See you then.

644
00:28:24,040 --> 00:28:25,560
Okay, bye!

645
00:28:41,600 --> 00:28:43,280
Nice one, Tao.

646
00:28:43,480 --> 00:28:45,720
Showing up in a luxury car now?

647
00:28:46,360 --> 00:28:47,960
Better to rely on yourself
than on anyone else.

648
00:28:48,360 --> 00:28:48,800
