657
00:29:13,640 --> 00:29:14,400
Don't worry.

658
00:29:14,880 --> 00:29:15,920
I promise I won't.

659
00:29:28,280 --> 00:29:29,080
Tao.

660
00:29:30,120 --> 00:29:31,320
Be careful on the way.

661
00:29:32,440 --> 00:29:33,440
Goodbye, Mr. Xiang.

662
00:29:33,560 --> 00:29:34,200
Bye.

663
00:29:51,560 --> 00:29:52,240
Li.

664
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:56,880
You've got a mule named Shen Taotao.

665
00:29:57,920 --> 00:29:58,360
