666
00:29:58,400 --> 00:29:59,720
The flight attendant.

667
00:30:00,120 --> 00:30:01,920
She's not moving cargo anymore.

668
00:30:03,280 --> 00:30:03,960
Right.

669
00:30:04,400 --> 00:30:06,360
She's never handling cargo again.

670
00:30:06,920 --> 00:30:07,800
I've got

671
00:30:07,880 --> 00:30:08,680
