679
00:30:32,320 --> 00:30:34,400
Stop that painting
before it leaves the country.

680
00:30:52,240 --> 00:30:54,400
Almighty Lord.

681
00:30:57,360 --> 00:30:59,000
Please bless me.

682
00:31:20,040 --> 00:31:21,440
Hello, China Customs.
Please cooperate with the inspection.

683
00:31:21,440 --> 00:31:22,320
Please cooperate with the inspection.

