00:31:40,680 --> 00:31:42,360
Hello, China Customs.
Please cooperate with the inspection.

685
00:31:47,240 --> 00:31:48,080
Excuse me, sir.

686
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:49,040
This way, please.

687
00:32:01,040 --> 00:32:01,680
Hello.

688
00:32:02,320 --> 00:32:03,960
China Customs.
Please cooperate with the inspection.

