693
00:32:23,240 --> 00:32:24,040
Copy that.

694
00:32:27,720 --> 00:32:29,280
Excuse me, sir.

695
00:32:29,520 --> 00:32:31,520
China Customs.
Please cooperate with the inspection.

696
00:32:31,520 --> 00:32:33,920
China Customs.
Please cooperate with the inspection.

