Too warm here?

699
00:32:59,240 --> 00:33:00,160
It's okay…

700
00:33:01,040 --> 00:33:01,920
Not at all.

701
00:33:22,600 --> 00:33:23,640
What's in here?

702
00:33:25,440 --> 00:33:26,960
Nothing…

703
