Liu, what's going on?

761
00:37:09,960 --> 00:37:11,360
- Liu! - Liu!

762
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:12,440
- Stop! - Stop!

763
00:37:12,440 --> 00:37:13,760
- Liu! - Liu!

764
00:37:13,960 --> 00:37:15,080
- Stop! - Don't run!

765
00:37:15,440 --> 00:37:16,600
Stop him!

766
00:37:16,720 --> 00:37:17,760
Grab him!

767
00:37:26,760 --> 00:37:27,760
Liu?

768
00:37:28,800 --> 00:37:29,800
Call Anti-Smuggling.

769
00:37:30,000 --> 00:37:30,640
Liu just came at us

770
00:37:30,640 --> 00:37:32,200
