would've been all over me.

773
00:37:35,040 --> 00:37:35,840
Bowen, are you okay?

774
00:37:36,600 --> 00:37:37,400
This is all my fault.

775
00:37:37,400 --> 00:37:38,680
I shouldn't have gone over there

776
00:37:38,680 --> 00:37:39,640
to see the painting.

777
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:40,400
Are you okay?

778
00:37:40,400 --> 00:37:41,720
- That burn looks bad. - I'm fine.

779
00:37:41,720 --> 00:37:43,040
Liu did it.

780
00:37:43,040 --> 00:37:43,680
Which Liu?

781
00:37:44,400 --> 00:37:45,320
Liu Kai?

782
00:37:45,760 --> 00:37:46,160
But…

783
00:37:46,160 --> 00:37:46,840
Hello.

784
00:37:46,840 --> 00:37:48,400
Mr. Li, go ahead.

785
00:37:50,600 --> 00:37:51,320
