Liu says he wants to see me.

788
00:37:55,120 --> 00:37:56,160
Gotta go down there.

789
00:37:56,520 --> 00:37:57,840
Get that burn treated.

790
00:37:58,800 --> 00:37:59,600
Put something on it.

791
00:38:01,040 --> 00:38:01,680
Dayu,

792
00:38:02,880 --> 00:38:04,520
go to the cafeteria, bring me

793
00:38:04,520 --> 00:38:05,360
Liu's favorite dishes.

794
00:38:05,520 --> 00:38:07,360
