Let's get him a good meal
before he goes.

796
00:38:09,800 --> 00:38:10,880
Grab some soup.

797
00:38:10,880 --> 00:38:11,680
His stomach isn't great.

798
00:38:15,120 --> 00:38:17,600
You really can't judge a person
by appearances.

799
