806
00:38:32,040 --> 00:38:33,000
And at the time,

807
00:38:33,000 --> 00:38:34,640
he was heading toward an outbound lane.

808
00:38:35,040 --> 00:38:35,840
So I'm guessing

809
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:38,040
the handler already
made it through customs,

810
00:38:38,040 --> 00:38:39,120
and is waiting for him outside.

811
00:38:39,880 --> 00:38:41,600
If we can't get Liu to talk,

812
00:38:41,600 --> 00:38:43,760
