813
00:38:43,800 --> 00:38:45,000
After that, he's gone for good.

814
00:38:45,800 --> 00:38:46,240
Alright.

815
00:38:46,640 --> 00:38:47,240
Let me try.

816
00:39:42,360 --> 00:39:43,040
Mr. Guo.

817
00:39:44,160 --> 00:39:44,720
I…

818
00:39:46,520 --> 00:39:47,360
I'm sorry.

819
