857
00:41:47,560 --> 00:41:48,800
Don't come back for now.

858
00:42:04,720 --> 00:42:05,520
Chen Wei.

859
00:42:05,800 --> 00:42:07,040
A distant relative of mine.

860
00:42:07,640 --> 00:42:09,480
He sent me money every year,

861
00:42:10,040 --> 00:42:11,640
but never asked me to do anything.

862
00:42:12,000 --> 00:42:12,760
This

863
00:42:12,960 --> 00:42:14,440
was the first time he ever used me.

864
00:42:14,520 --> 00:42:15,840
So Chen Wei was today's handler.

865
00:42:16,480 --> 00:42:18,000
He's the one
who gave you the pants, right?

866
00:42:18,360 --> 00:42:18,840
Yes.

867
00:42:26,920 --> 00:42:27,880
Justice has a long arm.

868
00:42:28,240 --> 00:42:29,280
None shall escape.

869
00:42:30,840 --> 00:42:32,040
No one gets away.

870
00:42:34,360 --> 00:42:35,480
After Chen Wei came to me,

871
00:42:35,720 --> 00:42:36,920
I started helping them

872
00:42:37,520 --> 00:42:38,960
keep tabs on Customs.

873
00:42:48,200 --> 00:42:49,440
I took that photo

874
00:42:49,800 --> 00:42:50,880
of Zhang Yu.

875
00:43:30,800 --> 00:43:37,360
♪There's a place of simple,
everyday warmth♪

876
00:43:38,280 --> 00:43:45,000
♪A door left open
for the wandering soul♪

877
00:43:45,920 --> 00:43:52,440
♪A humble table still warm with love♪

878
00:43:52,680 --> 00:43:56,320
♪After you've tasted every high and low♪

879
00:43:56,600 --> 00:44:00,240
♪Come home, I'll keep you warm♪

880
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:07,680
♪Where the days begin and end♪

881
00:44:08,440 --> 00:44:15,320
♪A light still on for the ones
who've lost their way♪

882
00:44:16,120 --> 00:44:22,680
♪An embrace waiting just for you♪

883
00:44:22,960 --> 00:44:26,680
♪Through every passing season♪

884
00:44:26,800 --> 00:44:30,480
♪Even if you return with nothing at all♪

885
00:44:31,120 --> 00:44:34,600
♪Turn around and look♪

886
00:44:34,800 --> 00:44:38,600
♪That door's still open♪

887
00:44:38,800 --> 00:44:42,440
♪A light still burning♪

888
00:44:42,520 --> 00:44:46,240
♪Waiting there for you♪

889
00:44:46,400 --> 00:44:49,920
♪Turn around and look♪

890
00:44:50,160 --> 00:44:53,960
♪Someone's still waiting♪

891
00:44:54,160 --> 00:44:57,760
♪Watching the dusk settle in♪

892
00:44:57,840 --> 00:45:01,560
♪Waiting for the break of dawn♪

893
00:45:03,320 --> 00:45:07,000
♪It's always there♪
